@723 = ~Good Luck~
@724 = ~Good Luck (Enchantment/Charm)
Level: 2
Range: 0
Duration: 2 rounds/level
Casting Time: 2
Area of Effect: caster
Saving Throw: none

The warlord who seeks to have a little luck can cast this spell. It slightly influences the course of events in favor of the spellcaster. Good luck can show in several ways, and help depends upon the level of caster.
Every round, a D6 determines how luck smiles to Warlord:
1: Nothing
2: Adverse blunder: bonus to AC
3: Luck: bonus to saving throws
4: Helpful observation: bonus to hit
5: Exceptional Strike: bonus to damage
6: Chance: additional attack and bonus to hit or damage.

The applied bonus is equal to +1 every 3 levels of the caster (maximum +5 at level 15).~
