@727 = ~Mirror Image~
@728 = ~Mirror Image (Illusion/Phantasm)
Level: 3
Range: 0
Duration: 5 round + 1 round/level
Casting Time: 3
Area of Effect: caster
Saving Throw: none

This spell makes appear several duplicates of the mage. The number of copies that appear depends upon the level:
Level 3 to 5  : 1D4
Level 6 to 8  : 1D6
Level 9 to 11 : 1D4+2
Level 12 to 14: 1D6+2
Level 15 to 17: 1D4+4
Level 18+     : 1D6+4
Those image do exactly what the wizard does. Since the spell causes a blurring and slight distortion when it is cast, it is impossible for opponents to be certain which are the illusions and which is the actual wizard. When an image is struck by a melee or missile attack, magical or otherwise, it disappears, but any other existing images remain intact until they are struck. However, it is important to note that this will not protect the caster against every attack as it is possible for an enemy to choose the real caster amongst all the images.~
